      <title>微软和英伟达将因人工智能举措面临美国反垄断调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/microsoft-nvidia-to-face-us-antitrust-probes-over-moves-in-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，美国两家反垄断机构已同意划分人工智能行业的职责，授权联邦贸易委员会对微软公司与 OpenAI 的关系展开调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/microsoft-nvidia-to-face-us-antitrust-probes-over-moves-in-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:22:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从墨西哥城到孟买，交易员们对选举意外感到震惊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/the-year-of-elections-is-burning-investors-from-mexico-to-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一凌晨，全球最赚钱的外汇交易之一因墨西哥大选出乎意料的转折而崩盘。20 小时后，印度投资者开始疯狂抛售股票，导致一天内市值蒸发 3860 亿美元，因为他们意识到自己严重误判了纳伦德拉·莫迪的选举胜利范围。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/the-year-of-elections-is-burning-investors-from-mexico-to-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿尔巴尼亚抗议活动愈演愈烈，要求总理辞职的呼声愈演愈烈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/albanian-protests-intensify-as-opposition-calls-on-rama-to-resign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一份意大利调查报告指控总理埃迪·拉马参与有组织犯罪和腐败之后，阿尔巴尼亚抗议者点燃轮胎并向警察投掷石块，要求总理埃迪·拉马辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/albanian-protests-intensify-as-opposition-calls-on-rama-to-resign</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:14:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
