      <title>比尔·黄、鲍勃·梅内德斯和一份 5 美元的沙拉：纽约法院奥斯卡颁奖典礼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bill-hwang-bob-menendez-and-a-5-salad-ny-s-courthouse-oscars</link>
